(250, NULL, 1, 242, 1, 1, 'Museum Canteen', 'museum-canteen', 'Museum Canteen', 'Museum Canteen', 'Museum Canteen', '<p>Museum Canteen</p>', '', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 4, NULL, 0, 'Museum Canteen', '2024-12-10 04:56:56', '2025-01-31 03:38:45'),
(251, NULL, 1, 250, 1, 1, 'Museum Shop', 'museum-shop', 'Museum Shop', 'Museum Shop', 'Museum Shop', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>The museum shop of IGRMS offers specialized and unique Art &amp; craft items to provide visitors with meaningful connections to culture, while also supporting artisans to promoting their sustainable practices. They are far more than souvenirs, serving as symbols of cultural heritage and offering visitors an opportunity to buy that samples of heritage for home. Two shops are presently available a) Near Avriti Bhawan, and (b) At the Reception Counter of the Indoor Museum (Veethi Sankul) where visitors can purchase Souvenirs including Museum publications.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', NULL, NULL, 3, 4, NULL, 0, 'pMuseum Shop/p', '2024-12-10 04:58:04', '2024-12-31 02:18:29'),
(252, NULL, 1, 250, 1, 1, 'Mothers Corner', 'mothers-corner', 'Mothers Corner', 'Mothers Corner', 'Mothers Corner', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>The Indoor Museum features a dedicated corner for lactating mothers and their children, ensuring a comfortable and supportive environment. This facility is located in Gallery No. 2 of the Indoor museum, providing a private space for mothers to attend to their infants while enjoying their visit to the museum.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', NULL, NULL, 3, 4, NULL, 0, 'pMothers Corner/p', '2024-12-10 04:58:37', '2024-12-31 02:19:17'),
(253, NULL, 1, 250, 1, 1, 'Wheel Chair', 'wheel-chair', 'Wheel Chair', 'Wheel Chair', 'Wheel Chair', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>IGRMS is committed to ensuring accessibility for all visitors, including those with physical challenges. The museum offers wheelchair facilities for easy access of physically challenged guests while exploring the Indoor Museum and in some of the open air exhibitions as well. Additionally, thoughtfully designed ramps provide easy access to all galleries, ensuring a comfortable and inclusive visit for everyone.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', NULL, NULL, 3, 4, NULL, 0, 'pWheel Chair/p', '2024-12-10 04:59:16', '2024-12-31 02:20:06'),
