(259, NULL, 1, 80, 1, 1, 'Friends of IGRMS Membership Form', 'friends-of-igrms-membership-form', 'Friends of IGRMS Membership Form', 'Friends of IGRMS Membership Form', 'Friends of IGRMS Membership Form', '<p>We invite you to become a part of an institution that is integral to Bhopal by joining or gifting the Friends of IGRMS membership. This membership supports the Museum&#39;s vital activities in the fields of education, outreach, conservation, publication and research. Friends of IGRMS have the opportunity to experience the Museum in a unique and special way with exclusive member benefits that include unlimited free admission, private tours, discounts at the Museum shop, and much more. Enjoy the privileges, enhance your experience and promote the future development of IGRMS by signing up for a membership category that is suitable for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Types of Membership </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1.</strong> Individual<strong> </strong>Membership&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Rs. 2000/- per annum</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Family Membership ( up to 4 members of a family)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Rs. 5000/- per annum</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Concessionary Membership (for senior citizens, staff of museums of Bhopal,&nbsp; students between age group of 13 and 21 years of age on basis of valid ID card)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Rs. 1000/- per annum</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;4. NGO/NPO/Private museums Membership</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Rs. 3000/- per annum</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5.&nbsp; Life Time Membership</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Rs. 10000/-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6.&nbsp; Corporate&nbsp; Membership (for a firm/team of professionals)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Rs. 20,000/- per annum</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7.&nbsp; Gifted Membership (all except family membership can be gifted)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8.&nbsp;&nbsp; Honorary Membership (for eminent persons)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Benefits/ Receivables</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 Membership card</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2 One time only introductory gift</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3 Unlimited free admission to the museum at Bhopal and its Southern Regional Centre at Mysore</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4 Introductory guided tour of the museum</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5 free access to all exhibitions and programmes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6 free access to reference library</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7 Free audio guide facility</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8 Free entry for morning and evening walk (beyond office hours)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9 Access to selfie points</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10 Invitation to all Programs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>11 News letter and event updates</p>\r\n\r\n<p>12&nbsp; 10% discount at museum shop, canteen, publications and venue/ facility bookings for conference, cultural programmes, photography and videography, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>13 Member exclusive event and behind the scene tours</p>\r\n\r\n<p>14 Access to priority seating at museum&rsquo;s public events</p>\r\n\r\n<p>15 50% discount on registration fee of &lsquo;Do and Learn&rsquo; Museum Education Programme</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Instructions &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 Every member of the &lsquo;Friends of the Museum&rsquo; program will receive an ID card. This must be shown at the Ticket counter or to the concerned staff member while availing of entry/discounts/ special privileges.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2 The Museum reserves the right to discontinue &amp; amend benefits/ reject applications/revoke Membership at its discretion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3 Recipient(s) of the gift Membership will need to submit their ID and address proof within a month of deposit of fee to confirm their membership.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4 Those opting for family Membership will need to provide names, ID card&nbsp; photographs, occupation&nbsp; and age for all Family members.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Terms and conditions</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1 </strong>Memberships are not refundable or transferable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2 Memberships categories and benefits are subject to change</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3 Members must present their Memberships card to avail of benefits.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4 Museum rules and regulations apply.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5 Benefits cannot be used in conjunction with any other special offer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6 In case of loss or damage of card, it can be reissued by paying a fee of Rs. 50/- and verification of ID proof.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Indira Gandhi Rashtriya Manav Sangrahalaya, Bhopal</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://125.20.102.85/igrms/public/upload/files/Indira Gandhi Rashtriya Manav Sangrahalaya_1738313682.pdf\"><strong>FRIENDS OF IGRMS: APPLICATION FOR MEMBERSHIP</strong></a></p>', '', '', NULL, NULL, 3, 4, NULL, 0, 'pFriends of IGRMS Membership Form/p', '2024-12-10 05:06:27', '2025-01-31 03:25:10'),
